msgctxt "56_Volcano Staff"
msgid "'Sup, Akiyama-san."
msgstr "Buenas, Akiyama-san."

msgctxt "68_Akiyama"
msgid "'Sup yourself. Working hard, I see."
msgstr "Buenas. Trabajando duro, ¿Eh?"

msgctxt "80_Volcano Staff"
msgid "Aw, my girl keeps bugging me－wants to go on a trip. But I'm\\r\n"
"working five days a week this month. I don't even have time\\r\n"
"for college."
msgstr "Bueno, mi chica esta quisquillosa con querer viajar.\\r\n"
"Este mes trabajo cinco días a la semana, así que\\r\n"
"no tengo tiempo para la universidad."

msgctxt "92_Akiyama"
msgid "Like you'd go if you had the time? Listen, I'm here to ask you a little favor. If you see this guy, let me know first thing, okay?"
msgstr "Aun si tuvieras tiempo, no irías a clases. Escucha,\\r\n"
"necesito que me hagas un favor.\\r\n"
"¿Podrías avisarme si ves a este tipo?"

msgctxt "104_Volcano Staff"
msgid "Ha! What the heck is this?"
msgstr "Ahh! ¿Que demonios es eso?"

msgctxt "116_Akiyama"
msgid "I'd like to meet with him if possible. Got some business to discuss."
msgstr "Tengo asuntos pendientes que discutir con él."

msgctxt "128_Volcano Staff"
msgid "And you think you're gonna find him with this? Whatever. If I\\r\n"
"see anybody who looks even remotely like this, I'll let you know."
msgstr "¿Y crees que vas a encontrarlo con esto? Como sea.\\r\n"
"Si veo a alguien que mas o menos se parezca, te lo haré saber."

msgctxt "140_Akiyama"
msgid "Thanks. I appreciate it."
msgstr "Gracias. Te lo agradezco."

msgctxt "152_Akiyama"
msgid "(I ought to show this flyer to the homeless guys on Park Boulevard. They've got a network all their own.)"
msgstr "(Debería enseñarle el boceto a los vagabundos del Parque Boulevard. Tienen una red de inteligencia.)"

